      *
     CSR         ESB710    ENDSR
      *---------------------------*
      * A-PICS 以外　調整枚数
      *---------------------------*
     CSR         #SB711    BEGSR
      *
     C           WKSRYO    DIV  20        W@KSSU  90
     C                     Z-ADD0         W@HAKD  51
     C           L1SYOS    IFNE 0
     C           W@KSSU    DIV  L1SYOS    W@HAKD
     C                     ENDIF
     C           W@HAKD    IFEQ 0
